text: José Velásquez (born 18 July 1970) is a Colombian former cyclist. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Colombia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
